{"tid":1256243,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美洲國家盃8強出爐，阿根廷或成最大贏家","createTime":"2019-06-25T02:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T05:34:51.000Z","uid":43785,"like":24,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8326e0000bee1ac48367311aad23e616ecfe637d","tid":1256243,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KPARuwb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKPARuwb.jpg&h=cfcd97c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實當阿根廷安排在B組第一場對哥倫比亞，已經知道被足總安排捧盃了，製造次名出線對阿根廷最有利，因為第一場慘負哥倫比亞，其後可以望住黎食。<br />\n<br />\n睇番B組首名出線哥倫比亞，要踢C組次名兩冠王智利，下場有機會對上烏拉圭，慘過食兩舊屎。<br />\nB組以次名出線阿根廷，只要踢A組次名委內瑞拉就能輕鬆上四強了。<br />\n<br />\n站在B組角度，次名出線才是最好。<br />\n因為A組只有巴西獨大。<br />\n所以A組次名較C組次名智利或烏拉圭難踢。<br />\n<br />\n所以落在B組，若以次名出線，就是8強賽的最大贏家。<br />\n此消彼長的關係，當其他隊被打得喘不過氣時，我們的球王美斯有足夠時間調整狀態。<br />\n<br />\n以最強的姿態迎戰沒有尼馬與委內瑞拉賽和的巴西及決賽<br />\n<br />\n相信美洲盃阿根廷及美斯或成最大贏家。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/twb9ggH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftwb9ggH.jpg&h=07f55f68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78652a28a9aad052fd3599fdcdeb922513cd0a56","tid":1256243,"uid":43785,"like":7,"dislike":14,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:08:34.000Z","msg":"好多人認為巴西好強， 其實只係錯誤嘅古老意識黎， 真正強嘅巴西已經沒落咗十幾年。<br />\n<br />\n依家嗰批人連波都唔識踢。 真正可以入到世界盃同美洲盃決賽嘅，係呢十年入面就只係得阿根廷呢一隊。<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家唔好中巴西毒， 巴西連委內瑞拉都贏唔到，只係打和咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff970c48dafff16617d229d989f1e661d829fef","tid":1256243,"uid":72476,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:10:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阿sir早晨</span></span>"},{"pid":"ad85fbbd237c439ac4a31eb0cc38ced187742bed","tid":1256243,"uid":268760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:12:37.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞先勁<br />\n阿鬥巴拉圭都係和波"},{"pid":"2d6c2fb3c7b05dc6693fe31923064691f0eced92","tid":1256243,"uid":18276,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:15:30.000Z","msg":"有人唔做去做狗"},{"pid":"5246c92b4106c52a8b541f5b4b4728b170275518","tid":1256243,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad85fbbd237c439ac4a31eb0cc38ced187742bed","tid":1256243,"uid":268760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:12:37.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞先勁<br />\n阿鬥巴拉圭都係和波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:15:57.000Z","msg":"阿根廷係望住條線嚟食， 唔畀自己首名。<br />\n特登用4分黎出線，唔想自己攞六分。<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知道 b組首名出線要對c組次名<br />\n所以不論今日贏嗰場係智利定烏拉圭,<br />\n8強都一定係一場惡鬥"},{"pid":"fed8722fefcd6b32e8cba415d6003f3261b67f77","tid":1256243,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"2d6c2fb3c7b05dc6693fe31923064691f0eced92","tid":1256243,"uid":18276,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:15:30.000Z","msg":"有人唔做去做狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:16:52.000Z","msg":"唔好做屈毛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba403bd9badb57b106e0b7e08898587243ea6c7","tid":1256243,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:32:39.000Z","msg":"支持美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9f587d26b41ec7bd2b1ad2e4b9e13b943ef0ab","tid":1256243,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"認真巴西弱左嫁啦有d傷左冇召到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38dc98aea3a26bfd36e358f6dbfc4a9b300614ff","tid":1256243,"uid":24997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201